  "body": "Deploying contracts one after the other leads to an error on the first run, but succeeds on subsequent runs.\r\nHappens independently of which forking url is used.\r\n\r\n - Create dummy contract\r\n - Configure hardhat to fork mainnet\r\n - Run hardhat node\r\n - Deploy 25x this dummy contract on localhost\r\n - Watch Transaction failed: revert error message\r\n\r\nMinimal reproduction\r\nhttps://github.com/tpscrpt/hardhat-deploy-repro\r\nReadme has instructions\r\nAdjusted gas so you can see the output in the node console",
