    "body": "> I used your repo, and it failed after the 14th deploy. I think it's this bug: #1231. Basically, the test mnemonic's account 0 has a contract creation transaction with nonce 14, so the 15th attempted deploy will revert. After that however, the nonce has been incremented past the problematic number, so the subsequent creations work.\r\n\r\nYeah setting index to 1 fixed this",
